						<summary>

						<p>This inscription is dated <hi rend="bold">Chāḷukya-Vikrama year 3[1, Vya]ya, [Śrāva]ṇa, śu. 1[0], Thursday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1106, July 12, Thursday.</hi> It records the death of Chāva-Gāvuṇḍa and Holli-Gāvuṇḍa in a battle on the occasion of a campaign on Nīlagunde by <hi rend="bold">Chāgaladēvi,</hi> wife of a Mahāsāmanta (name lost) of <hi rend="bold">Toṟagale.</hi></p>						

